Dia. 01 Wishful Thinking
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White might think he can simply play the dansu at 1 and he doesn't need any vital point.
\par
\par If Black plays at 2, White can easily win the capturing race with 3.
\par However it is just White's \cf1\b wishful thinking\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par Black is not going to connect at 2.
\par
\par
\par }
